@startuml multi-machine-no-sync
title Without sync: each machine holds its own truth

skinparam monochrome false
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #666
    RoundCorner 6
}

rectangle "🖥️  Laptop\n.beads/\n  bd-101 open\n  bd-102 done\n  bd-103 in_progress" as L #D9EDFF
rectangle "🖥️  Dev VM\n.beads/\n  bd-101 open\n  bd-104 open\n  bd-105 in_progress" as V #D9EDFF
rectangle "🖥️  Cron box\n.beads/\n  bd-101 open\n  bd-106 blocked" as C #D9EDFF

L -right[#C92A2A,thickness=2]-> V : no sync\ndiverged\n
V -right[#C92A2A,thickness=2]-> C : no sync\ndiverged

note bottom
  Three different views. Laptop agent does not see VM's bd-104.
  VM closes a task; cron keeps working on it. No shared truth.
end note

@enduml
